title: SET_REACTION_TO_VEHICLE_WITH_SIREN_DISABLED
content:
0xB90BBC6E// SetReactionToVehicleWithSirenDisabled
void SET_REACTION_TO_VEHICLE_WITH_SIREN_DISABLED(BOOL state);Parameters:state: Toggle on or off.This completely disables pedestrian vehicles from reacting to sirens. They will not try to do any maneuver to evade.
